oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM's Cedarcrest Jamboree, originally broadcast 1952-11, day unknown, first 8 minutes only. Featuring Carl Smith, Bobby Foster (steel guitar), Little Jimmy Dickens, and Grady Martin (fiddle). Also mentioned as being on the show but not present on this excerpt is Minnie Pearl.
